{"tid":197411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"話女學生抵死嘅人﹐覺得衝燈係罪無可恕","createTime":"2017-04-12T00:23:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T14:44:11.000Z","uid":25643,"like":20,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"039245050e093494abc92ee326e447ee914f5f3d","tid":197411,"uid":25643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T00:23:51.000Z","msg":"毋須爭拗衝燈社會道德上有冇錯﹐因為一定有<br />\n<br />\n問題只係呢個錯﹐大家認為要受幾大懲戒<br />\n<br />\n學生妹死咗﹐本來已經係最大懲戒<br />\n<br />\n亦遠超社會一貫接受嘅懲戒: 罰錢<br />\n<br />\n因此對死者繼續口誅筆伐﹐代表部分連登仔覺得<br />\n<br />\n死都唔夠懲治呢條仆街﹐起碼要搞埋佢屋企人﹐<br />\n<br />\n先可以洩心頭之憤。<br />\n<br />\n為配合連登仔嘅道德高地﹐建議以後亂過馬路判處即時槍斃﹐亂抛垃圾入獄十年。噉樣就可以息眾怒唔使嘈嘈閉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd7272d3896f5b31adf1753eca8346b152cdfe7","tid":197411,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T00:38:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ffb839ab1107fcf7e3c8f98f173853a4330d039","tid":197411,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T00:39:51.000Z","msg":"喂，連登仔唔衝燈架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3528e1040c3495deb15107a42253ec8501fa10e","tid":197411,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T00:42:38.000Z","msg":"btw，連登變到咁撚低質，你話無支共搞事都無人信<br />\n不過總有班死蠢易受5毛影響，反stereotype，無眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe93420bc1ec2bb7da00338ae00e92cf40d7952","tid":197411,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T00:46:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喂，連登仔唔衝燈架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我沖燈比車車死未又係比高登仔開post笑<br />\n<br />\n多魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d950eef5e6a1e133d8ae8f6ca4523a0cca50b487","tid":197411,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12